  <div id="dont" class="hello" style="display: none;"><p>You don’t need to tell DVLA unless your treatment changes to insulin or you don't feel safe when you drive.</p></div>
    <div id="tell" class="hello" style="display: none;"><p class="notify">You must tell DVLA if you have diabetes. <a href"https://www.gov.uk/driving-medical-conditions">Tell DVLA</a> if this affects you or someone you know.</p></div>

